DEUTSCHE BANK NATIONAL TRUST COMPANY, AS TRUSTEE FOR the REGISTERED HOLDER OF MORGAN STANLEY HOME EQUITY LOAN TRUST 2007-2 MORTGAGE PASS THROUGH CERTIFICATES, Series 2007-2, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Wayne PASCHALL and Mrs. Paschall, Unknown Spouse of Wayne Paschall, Defendant-Petitioner. C-499 September Term 2018
081603 Supreme Court of New Jersey. JANUARY 18, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001828-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
